    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an impeccable 997.1 Carrera S, a masterclass in analog feedback and mechanical harmony. This example features the 3.8L flat-six powerplant, delivering a linear torque curve and a visceral 7,200 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission is paired with a factory short-shift kit for tactile, bolt-action gear changes. Chassis dynamics are optimized via Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a mechanical limited-slip differential, ensuring flat cornering and superb lateral grip. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained with a documented IMS bearing upgrade and zero bore scoring. The factory finish remains flawless, and the interior retains its showroom-fresh matte texture, free of typical UV degradation or bolster wear.",
