      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that has been meticulously maintained and garage-kept since day one. The exterior features original, high-gloss paint protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring a mirror-like finish free of rock chips or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' condition; the premium leather seats are supple and free of wear, the dashboard is pristine, and it has never been smoked in. Mechanically, this car is flawless. It comes with a complete, documented service history, including a recent major service and a fresh set of high-performance tires with 90% tread remaining. Every feature, from the immersive premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks, smells, and drives like it just rolled off the assembly line. Serious inquiries only.",
